<blockquote class="gmail_quote" style="margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex;">Le 12/09/2011 12:52, Gabriele Fatigati a écrit :<br>
<div class="im">&gt; Dear hwloc users,<br>
